00:25:19,281 --> 00:25:21,952
I already tried that.

362
00:25:21,987 --> 00:25:22,917
我已经尝试了

363
00:25:23,259 --> 00:25:26,383
Real quiet out there.
Did you send out a call? 只有一个回应。 回应怎么说？

364
00:25:26,627 --> 00:25:29,076
Wouldn't be safe.
没有人是安全的。

365
00:25:29,264 --> 00:25:29,798
No! I know what you're thinking
and it's not possible.

366
00:25:29,833 --> 00:25:34,428
好吧，我知道你在想什么，这不可能，
这样的事情根本不可能在这里发生

367
00:25:34,428 --> 00:25:34,463
Absolutely, completely impossible.

368
00:25:34,463 --> 00:25:37,483
That kind of stuff just doesn't
happen here. Not in this country.

369
00:25:37,518 --> 00:25:37,588
不可能在这个国家。
还是小心为妙。

370
00:25:37,588 --> 00:25:40,757
We gotta be careful.
It could be a lot at stake here.

371
00:25:40,890 --> 00:25:44,209
She's right. We've got to assume something
bad has happened. 她是对的 我们已经看到过坏事发生了。

372
00:25:44,315 --> 00:25:47,442
Of course something bad has
happened. My dog is dead. 当然是坏事了，我的狗死了。

373
00:25:47,548 --> 00:25:50,922
I didn't mean it like that. Shut up!
Everyone shut up! 我不是这个意思。 所有闭嘴。闭嘴！

374
00:25:51,028 --> 00:25:54,243
Jesus Christ, what is going on?
天哪，会发生什么？

375
00:25:57,193 --> 00:26:00,559
Kevin's place was next.
I don't remember who suggested it,

376
00:26:00,594 --> 00:26:00,667
凯文家是下一个，我记不得是谁建议这样做

377
00:26:00,667 --> 00:26:04,253
but we decided to
stay off the main roads.

378
00:26:04,288 --> 00:26:08,288
我们决定避开大路，走小道

379
00:26:09,872 --> 00:26:12,615
Mom! Dad! Mitchell!
妈妈，爸爸，米切尔。 弗林特。

380
00:26:14,889 --> 00:26:16,921
Flip?

381
00:26:18,988 --> 00:26:21,142
Flip!
弗林特。

382
00:26:25,021 --> 00:26:29,556
Looks alright. -He always has a bucket of food and
some water. Don't you, boy? 看起来不错。 你饿坏了吧，小子？

383
00:26:30,750 --> 00:26:34,266
你不能带上它
你觉得我会把它丢下么？

384
00:26:34,266 --> 00:26:34,301
You can't bring that.

385
00:26:34,301 --> 00:26:38,536
You think I'm just gonna leave
him here? I'm not leaving him!

386
00:26:38,571 --> 00:26:39,208
凯文
你觉得我会把它丢下么？

387
00:26:39,208 --> 00:26:40,458
凯文，嘿，嘿，嘿！

388
00:26:40,493 --> 00:26:40,923
Stop it!

389
00:26:40,958 --> 00:26:43,250
住手！
我不会离开它的。

390
00:26:43,285 --> 00:26:44,409
I'm not leaving him!

391
00:26:45,810 --> 00:26:48,491
He's got a point.
他是对的。

392
00:26:52,616 --> 00:26:56,395
Let's take Flip to Corrie's and then we can
make another decision 嘿，先把它带到车上，然后再想其他的办法。

393
00:26:56,501 --> 00:27:00,146
depending on what we
find there. Agreed?

394
00:27:00,181 --> 00:27:02,443
好吗？

395
00:27:02,443 --> 00:27:05,393
Flip, let's go.
弗林特，我们走

396
00:27:13,309 --> 00:27:15,614
C'mon.
走吧！

397
00:27:21,721 --> 00:27:25,190
That's four out of four. The rest
of you live in town. 只有4.4英里，离我们最近的城市

398
00:27:25,295 --> 00:27:28,926
Robyn's house is on Coachman's Lane. That's
probably the closest. 我们可以去看看 莱恩小姐，她是离我们最近的。

399
00:27:29,032 --> 00:27:32,462
Yeah, you can see most of Wirrawee from the hill at
the back. 是的，我们可以去那个从山上看到的城市。 我们会发现什么的

400
00:27:32,588 --> 00:27:36,147
It might tell us something.
Then we go to Robyn's next.

401
00:27:36,182 --> 00:27:40,182
路上先去罗宾的家

402
00:27:58,728 --> 00:27:59,215
Flip, sit. Stay.

403
00:27:59,250 --> 00:28:01,833
弗林特坐下，待在这儿。

404
00:28:04,902 --> 00:28:09,156
Please don't touch that.
Let's go up that hill. 请不要去碰它。 我们到小山上去看看。

405
00:28:19,065 --> 00:28:20,173
Something's going on
at the Showground.

406
00:28:20,208 --> 00:28:21,719
下面发生了什么？
很可能就是人们在那里

407
00:28:21,754 --> 00:28:25,086
I think that's where everyone is.
What about those other lights?

408
00:28:25,121 --> 00:28:26,552
嗯，那些光呢？
那是医院使用紧急发电机。

409
00:28:26,587 --> 00:28:27,984
Hospital. Must be using
the emergency generators.

410
00:28:28,102 --> 00:28:29,132
Maybe we should split up.

411
00:28:29,167 --> 00:28:30,285
我想我们应该分开行动。
分开？

412
00:28:30,320 --> 00:28:31,465
Split up? No, we can't.
We have to stay together.

413
00:28:31,500 --> 00:28:35,125
不，我们！我们要在一起。
我们要去那里，在黎明之前

414
00:28:35,160 --> 00:28:36,693
We need to be out of town
before dawn. Just in case.

415
00:28:36,708 --> 00:28:38,227
去搞清楚所有的状况

416
00:28:38,227 --> 00:28:42,456
I'll take Fi to her house. Lee, you take Robyn
to yours. 我和菲菲回家去找些补给 李，你带上罗宾。

417
00:28:42,666 --> 00:28:45,842
We'll meet back here at 5 a.m.

418
00:28:45,877 --> 00:28:46,337
我们早上5点再集合。

419
00:28:46,372 --> 00:28:49,032
So we just stay here?
嗯，我们只是坐在这里吗？

420
00:28:52,859 --> 00:28:56,012
You get to go to the Show.

421
00:28:56,047 --> 00:29:00,047
你要去表演一下。

422
00:29:12,991 --> 00:29:16,218
Whose voices are those?
I don't know.

423
00:29:16,253 --> 00:29:17,970
谁的声音？
我不知道。

424
00:29:17,970 --> 00:29:21,140
I think we should go back.
No. Wait.

425
00:29:21,175 --> 00:29:22,676
我不想死。
不，等等！

426
00:29:22,676 --> 00:29:25,447
We have to get a better
look before we leave.

427
00:29:25,482 --> 00:29:25,553
在我们离开之前，我们得搞清楚状况

428
00:29:25,553 --> 00:29:27,636
Better look at what, Ellie? Let's go! 随便看看就行了，艾莉我们走吧。
我们之中必须要有人去打探更多的消息，在我们走之前。

429
00:29:27,741 --> 00:29:31,726
One of us has to get closer before
we go. We gotta see what's going on.

430
00:29:32,139 --> 00:29:35,057
I'm not leaving Corrie here.
嗯，我不想在这里被抓住。

431
00:29:38,454 --> 00:29:41,340
I'll
go. Ellie! 我去。

432
00:29:41,375 --> 00:29:43,042
艾莉

433
00:29:43,657 --> 00:29:47,048
If anything happens, run.
如果有什么事发生，跑。

434
00:30:49,552 --> 00:30:53,328
Do not try to escape
or you will be shot.

435
00:31:11,792 --> 00:31:13,875
你们所有的人。

436
00:31:19,408 --> 00:31:20,725
Dad!

437
00:31:20,760 --> 00:31:21,942
爸爸。

438
00:31:21,977 --> 00:31:26,061
This is bloody ridiculous. I've been
waiting in this stupid line for 2 hours!

439
00:31:26,096 --> 00:31:26,166
这太荒谬的，草泥马

440
00:31:26,166 --> 00:31:29,234
Who do you people think you are?

441
00:31:29,269 --> 00:31:29,542
你到底想从我们这里要什么？

442
00:31:29,542 --> 00:31:31,034
放开我。

443
00:31:31,069 --> 00:31:33,200
Hands off me.

444
00:31:38,708 --> 00:31:39,750
（隐约听出了广东话：带下去？）

445
00:32:29,037 --> 00:32:31,558
Are you okay?
你没事吧？

446
00:32:32,311 --> 00:32:33,572
Where's Kevin?

447
00:32:33,607 --> 00:32:34,833
凯文在哪儿？

448
00:32:37,805 --> 00:32:39,215
Quick! They're coming!

449
00:32:39,250 --> 00:32:40,625
他们来了，他们来了，来了！

450
00:32:42,561 --> 00:32:44,530
Ellie... -What?
Can we stop?

451
00:32:44,565 --> 00:32:46,458
艾莉
什么？等一下。

452
00:32:46,493 --> 00:32:48,351
Corrie, c'mon! Please! Please.

453
00:32:48,386 --> 00:32:49,695
快点，快点

454
00:32:49,695 --> 00:32:51,751
Come on.

455
00:32:52,646 --> 00:32:55,867
Where are they now?
I don't know. -Guys!

456
00:32:55,902 --> 00:32:55,973
上帝啊！
你在做什么？

457
00:32:55,973 --> 00:32:58,090
Kevin! Oh my God!
What happened to you?

458
00:32:58,125 --> 00:33:00,783
凯文，你是怎么了？
嗯，他们看到你，所以我就跑了啊。

459
00:33:00,818 --> 00:33:03,442
I thought that you're ahead of me,
so I just... I just ran.

460
00:33:04,829 --> 00:33:08,210
Ellie said that if anything was
to happen to run. 艾莉说了一旦发生什么事，就跑

461
00:33:11,961 --> 00:33:14,460
Oh my God!
Go!

462
00:33:14,495 --> 00:33:14,708
他们来了。

463
00:33:23,542 --> 00:33:25,827
C'mon, c'mon...
快跑，快跑。

464
00:33:26,595 --> 00:33:27,714
Let's go.

465
00:33:27,749 --> 00:33:28,833
跑跑跑。

466
00:33:30,333 --> 00:33:33,515
I hurt my knee.
C'mon, we gotta keep moving.

467
00:33:33,550 --> 00:33:36,582
我的膝盖
快，快 不要停下来

468
00:33:36,582 --> 00:33:39,722
Are you alright?
No. I cut it. Jesus! 你还好吗？不好。

469
00:33:46,721 --> 00:33:49,219
Give me your shirt.
Quick. 我需要你的衬衫。 好。

470
00:33:49,325 --> 00:33:53,913
Singlet, it's better. Quick. Get
me a stick or something. 背心更好。 好。

471
00:33:56,059 --> 00:33:58,480
Stay here.
待在这里。

472
00:34:06,594 --> 00:34:07,484
Ellie, hurry up!

473
00:34:07,519 --> 00:34:08,375
艾莉，快点。

474
00:34:12,871 --> 00:34:15,250
Quick, get back!

475
00:34:18,480 --> 00:34:21,556
Will this do? -
Yeah, quick. 这是什么？闭嘴。

476
00:34:22,835 --> 00:34:25,930
Ellie, they are coming.
Alright. 他们来了，他们来了。 好。

477
00:34:28,807 --> 00:34:30,912
Light it.

478
00:34:33,796 --> 00:34:35,935
Light it.
蛋定点儿！

479
00:34:52,833 --> 00:34:53,930
起来，宝贝，
艾莉，我们走

480
00:34:53,965 --> 00:34:58,723
Corrie, we gotta get out of here.
Get up, c'mon. Ellie, let's go!

481
00:35:04,864 --> 00:35:07,060
Hang up.
撑住

482
00:35:11,448 --> 00:35:14,472
She wasn't much older than I was.
她跟我年龄差不多，也跟我同样害怕

483
00:35:14,787 --> 00:35:17,899
And she looked just as scared.

484
00:35:29,455 --> 00:35:30,090
I'll never forget her.

485
00:35:30,125 --> 00:35:36,125
我永远不会忘记她。
艾莉，我们没有多少时间了

486
00:35:36,160 --> 00:35:39,194
Ellie, we don't have time.
Come on!

487
00:35:39,194 --> 00:35:40,173
Thank God!
We heard an explosion.

488
00:35:40,208 --> 00:35:44,792
感谢上帝，我们遇到了爆炸！
是的，我们是。

489
00:35:44,827 --> 00:35:45,820
Yeah, that was us.
Are you alright? -Yeah.

490
00:35:46,903 --> 00:35:50,072
Flip! There he is. Good boy!

491
00:35:50,107 --> 00:35:50,458
弗林特，好孩子。

492
00:35:50,594 --> 00:35:53,927
Where did all those
soldiers come from?

493
00:35:57,811 --> 00:36:00,856
Where did you get this thing?
从哪儿搞到的这玩意儿？

494
00:36:05,095 --> 00:36:05,840
Wait, where's Robyn and Lee?

495
00:36:05,875 --> 00:36:09,463
罗宾和李在哪里？
他们还没有回来了。

496
00:36:09,498 --> 00:36:13,052
They haven't come back yet.
It's almost 6 a.m.

497
00:36:13,087 --> 00:36:14,528
我们等到早上6点，大家都放弃了，
就回来了。

498
00:36:14,563 --> 00:36:15,970
We were just about
to give up on all of you.

499
00:36:16,077 --> 00:36:19,162
We have to go and find them then,
don't we? -Ellie... （好大一把仿AK47的国产56式冲锋枪）

500
00:36:19,167 --> 00:36:19,288
我必须去找到他们。
艾莉

501
00:36:19,288 --> 00:36:20,008
Homer, we have to go find them.
It's daylight now.

502
00:36:20,008 --> 00:36:20,043
荷马必须找到他们。
马上站住!

503
00:36:20,043 --> 00:36:22,718
（国产56式冲锋枪曾经是解放军标志性武器配备，曾大批量服役，
不过现在解放军所使用的是99式冲锋枪）

504
00:36:22,753 --> 00:36:25,393
I'm not leaving them. We're not leaving
them. 我不会放弃他们。 我们都不会放弃他们！

505
00:36:25,503 --> 00:36:27,878
We'll come back tonight
when it's safer. 我们晚上再回去，更安全些。

506
00:36:27,985 --> 00:36:31,232
Yeah cause there'll be soldiers
crawling all over town by now.

507
00:36:31,267 --> 00:36:33,875
是的，现在满城市都是士兵，尤其是在她所作所为之后。

508
00:36:33,910 --> 00:36:34,318
I mean... after what you did.

509
00:36:35,978 --> 00:36:40,125
We will find them.
Ellie, I promise.

510
00:36:40,160 --> 00:36:40,333
我会找到他们，艾莉。我保证。

511
00:37:01,833 --> 00:37:05,968
El... El...
come on. 小艾，小艾 嗯

512
00:37:06,003 --> 00:37:07,750
来吧。

513
00:37:14,347 --> 00:37:17,223
Wait, just...
No, don't touch me.

514
00:37:17,258 --> 00:37:17,375
来。
不，不要碰我。

515
00:37:26,936 --> 00:37:30,234
Sit down over there.
Are you alright? 坐在那里吧 你还好吧？

516
00:37:30,502 --> 00:37:33,682
I'll get us some food.
Thank you.

517
00:37:33,717 --> 00:37:34,333
我拿些吃的。
谢谢你。

518
00:37:36,724 --> 00:37:37,298
So, any idea whose army it is?
We didn't exactly stop to ask.

519
00:37:37,333 --> 00:37:40,179
关于军队，你们有什么想法么？
你可以不可以停下来，别老问这么多问题

520
00:37:40,214 --> 00:37:43,353
We'll ask Robyn. She's good with flags
and things like that. 去问罗宾吧，她肯定对这些感兴趣的

521
00:37:43,458 --> 00:37:45,257
All I can say is they are not greek.
It doesn't matter who they are,

522
00:37:45,257 --> 00:37:45,292
我只能说，他们不是希腊人。

523
00:37:45,292 --> 00:37:49,167
他们是谁不重要，因为他们已经在这里了。
重要的是我们该怎么办

524
00:37:49,202 --> 00:37:49,237
because they're here.
We just got to deal with it.

525
00:37:49,237 --> 00:37:49,548
Alright, mate. Calm down.

526
00:37:49,583 --> 00:37:54,167
好吧，冷静点儿。
都已经这样还管他妈什么旗标呢。

527
00:37:54,202 --> 00:37:58,202
No, seriously, what difference
does a flag make?

528
00:38:23,524 --> 00:38:26,510
Fi made this for you.
菲菲给你做了这个。

529
00:38:32,057 --> 00:38:35,055
Her house is empty too?
Yeah.

530
00:38:35,090 --> 00:38:35,901
之后你们发生了？

531
00:38:35,936 --> 00:38:38,301
There are soldiers everywhere.

532
00:38:38,336 --> 00:38:38,636
我们用了各种方式回到这里。

533
00:38:38,671 --> 00:38:41,582
We crawled all the way
back to Robyn's.

534
00:38:42,131 --> 00:38:45,100
Not bad for a first date.
不算坏的第一天

535
00:38:55,854 --> 00:38:58,990
The others told me what happened.

536
00:38:59,025 --> 00:39:00,356
有人告诉我发生了什么。

537
00:39:00,356 --> 00:39:02,231
El.
艾莉

538
00:39:03,180 --> 00:39:05,768
It's not your fault.
这不是你的错，不是

539
00:39:06,074 --> 00:39:09,801
It's not your fault.
It's theirs.

540
00:39:09,836 --> 00:39:10,583
都是他们的错

541
00:39:11,134 --> 00:39:14,330
It's all theirs.

542
00:39:14,365 --> 00:39:16,123
都是他们的

543
00:39:16,123 --> 00:39:19,053
You're changing.
Yeah? 你变了

544
00:39:20,877 --> 00:39:25,614
For better or worse?
Better. Definitely better.

545
00:39:25,649 --> 00:39:25,684
更好了还是更差了
更好了

546
00:39:25,684 --> 00:39:27,125
毫无疑问，更好了

547
00:40:06,645 --> 00:40:08,031
Looks good.

548
00:40:08,066 --> 00:40:09,417
看起来好点儿了

549
00:40:09,506 --> 00:40:12,690
Fi'd always say she'd
be a doctor. 坐下来，可能会好点儿

550
00:40:22,491 --> 00:40:26,265
You're gonna have to forgive him
sooner or later, you know.

551
00:40:26,300 --> 00:40:26,778
迟早你都得原谅他，你知道吗？

552
00:40:26,778 --> 00:40:29,717
He just left us, Ellie.
他就这样丢下我们，艾莉。

553
00:40:30,805 --> 00:40:33,795
He just ran and left us.
逃跑，丢下了我们。

554
00:40:35,301 --> 00:40:38,308
I thought he loved me.
我以为他爱我。

555
00:40:39,541 --> 00:40:43,344
Do you remember how many
hours we used to spend up here?

556
00:40:43,379 --> 00:40:43,542
你还记得我们在这里度过多少个小时么？

557
00:40:43,621 --> 00:40:44,132
You mean the tea parties?

558
00:40:44,167 --> 00:40:50,625
你的意思是茶话会呢？
我们以前是如此纯真。

559
00:40:50,660 --> 00:40:50,965
We were so innocent
back then. And now I...

560
00:40:51,000 --> 00:40:53,474
现在我觉得昨天所做的并非是，
天真的人才能做得出来的。

561
00:40:53,509 --> 00:40:55,949
I feel like we were innocent
right up until yesterday.

562
00:40:56,452 --> 00:40:59,880
We didn't believe in Santa Claus
or anything like that.

563
00:40:59,915 --> 00:40:59,995
上帝啊，我可不相信什么圣诞老人之类的。

564
00:40:59,995 --> 00:41:03,297
You know, we believed
in other fantasies.

565
00:41:03,332 --> 00:41:03,960
我们沉迷于一个个幻想中

566
00:41:03,960 --> 00:41:05,271
We believed we were safe.

567
00:41:05,306 --> 00:41:06,583
我们自以为我们是安全的。

568
00:41:09,665 --> 00:41:13,647
I guess that was the biggest
fantasy of them all, right?

569
00:41:13,682 --> 00:41:15,296
这是最大的幻想，对不对？

570
00:41:15,296 --> 00:41:19,160
Do you ever think we'll see
Robyn and Lee again?

571
00:41:19,195 --> 00:41:20,083
你认为我们会再见到罗宾和李呢？

572
00:41:28,923 --> 00:41:30,274
That's one of ours!

573
00:41:30,309 --> 00:41:31,625
那是我们的一架飞机

574
00:41:32,225 --> 00:41:35,083
（一架澳军现役主力美制F-18战机）

575
00:41:36,083 --> 00:41:46,225
（三架国产歼十战机，注意看中间那架，驾驶舱下面的进气口，
那是歼十标志性的特征之一，导演在告诉我们歼十：F18=3：1）

576
00:41:54,897 --> 00:41:55,840
How many planes do we have?

577
00:41:55,875 --> 00:41:59,958
我们有多少架飞机？
现在少了一架。

578
00:41:59,993 --> 00:42:00,773
One less now.

579
00:42:01,673 --> 00:42:02,298
How's this?

580
00:42:02,333 --> 00:42:03,703
这样吧，我和艾莉去找罗宾和李。

581
00:42:03,738 --> 00:42:06,781
I'm going to Wirrawee with Ellie
and we look for Robyn and Lee.

582
00:42:06,886 --> 00:42:09,846
You three go back to my place and load up the Landrover.
你们三个，去我家给陆虎加上油 去那儿可要冒很大的风险呢

583
00:42:09,952 --> 00:42:12,404
Seems a hell of a risk
going back into Wirrawee.

584
00:42:12,510 --> 00:42:15,684
What if it was you they're
going back for? 如果你跟他们去城镇呢？

585
00:42:16,083 --> 00:42:18,558
Don't ask me to go with you.
He's not.

586
00:42:18,593 --> 00:42:18,664
有可能哦。

587
00:42:18,664 --> 00:42:20,851
Good, because I'm not
bloody going. 不会。 那我哪儿也不去

588
00:42:20,955 --> 00:42:23,825
Jesus, Kevin. Everything is a risk from
now on. 上帝啊，凯文，从现在开始做任何事都会有风险。

589
00:42:23,931 --> 00:42:28,989
We can't sit around here forever. The biggest risk is
to take no risk. 我们不能永远呆在这里。 最大的风险就是不冒这个险。

590
00:42:29,934 --> 00:42:34,766
Alright. But if we can't stay here
where do you want us all to go?

591
00:42:34,801 --> 00:42:35,208
好的，但如果我们不能待在这里，
我们将去哪儿呢？

592
00:42:37,019 --> 00:42:39,027
Hell.
地狱。

593
00:42:39,341 --> 00:42:42,669
We're not taking your teddies.
Not all of them, just one.

594
00:42:42,704 --> 00:42:42,775
我们不能带首饰
并不是所有，只带一个。

595
00:42:42,775 --> 00:42:45,780
We can't take things like that.
Why can't we? 不能这样 为什么不呢？

596
00:42:45,885 --> 00:42:49,471
This isn't a picnic, El. We have to start acting
like soldiers. 这不是去野餐，我们必须开始表现得像个士兵。

597
00:42:49,889 --> 00:42:53,506
One mistake and... it's all over.

598
00:42:53,541 --> 00:42:55,083
一着不慎满盘皆输

599
00:42:55,893 --> 00:42:59,805
Can we take my mom's crowns and sashes?
Yeah, and photos. Don't forget photos.

600
00:42:59,840 --> 00:43:01,184
我得带上我妈妈的首饰。
还有相片。

601
00:43:01,219 --> 00:43:02,528
Geez, we're gonna need
a trailer pretty soon.

602
00:43:02,634 --> 00:43:06,175
Look, if you can take teddies, crowns and
photos, 要带首饰和皇冠，我为什么不 带上我父亲的足球奖杯呢。

603
00:43:06,304 --> 00:43:10,217
I might aswell take my dad's
bloody football trophies.

604
00:43:15,877 --> 00:43:19,287
Oh, and dog food for Flip.
Lots of dog food. Write that down.

605
00:43:19,322 --> 00:43:19,393
还有狗食，我狗狗的狗食，写下来

606
00:43:19,393 --> 00:43:22,154
He can eat rabbit.
What about wire cutters?

607
00:43:22,189 --> 00:43:22,259
我们需要帐篷，和洗漱什么的。

608
00:43:22,259 --> 00:43:25,043
Now that's a great idea.
这是一个好主意。

609
00:43:26,952 --> 00:43:28,247
Two T's.

610
00:43:28,282 --> 00:43:29,542
真贴心

611
00:43:42,903 --> 00:43:45,548
What about guns?
We'll take our own guns. 武器呢？我们需要武器 把它关掉

612
00:43:45,654 --> 00:43:48,537
Just turn it off.
No, I can fix this. Hang on.

613
00:43:48,572 --> 00:43:48,958
我可以修好它。

614
00:43:51,923 --> 00:43:54,556
The pipe's burst again.
被堵住了

615
00:43:59,024 --> 00:44:01,767
So, we've got plenty of
ammo for the rifles,

616
00:44:01,802 --> 00:44:03,625
我们有弹药充足的来复枪和看不完的杂志。

617
00:44:03,660 --> 00:44:04,372
and a full magazine for that.

618
00:44:04,625 --> 00:44:05,521
I got it!

619
00:44:05,556 --> 00:44:06,417
弄好了

620
00:44:11,411 --> 00:44:12,705
What's that?

621
00:44:12,740 --> 00:44:14,000
那是什么？

622
00:44:17,439 --> 00:44:20,301
We forgot to have someone on watch.

623
00:44:20,333 --> 00:44:20,610
我们忘了还有人在巡逻。

624
00:44:20,610 --> 00:44:23,501
Don't touch the curtains.

625
00:44:23,536 --> 00:44:25,055
不要碰窗帘

626
00:44:25,055 --> 00:44:27,853
Spread out!
Go into different rooms.

627
00:44:27,888 --> 00:44:27,959
快散开到不同的房间里去。

628
00:44:27,959 --> 00:44:31,695
If you see anything, yell out. But
stay hidden. 如果发现什么，不要乱动，给我安静地待好了

629
00:44:35,917 --> 00:44:37,625
Flip!
弗林特。

630
00:44:37,932 --> 00:44:40,474
Flip, get inside!
弗林特快进去

631
00:44:50,199 --> 00:44:52,907
It's here!

632
00:44:53,533 --> 00:44:54,433
Did they see you?
I don't know.

633
00:44:54,468 --> 00:44:55,333
我看见你了吗？
我不知道。

634
00:45:28,307 --> 00:45:29,528
Homer!

635
00:45:29,563 --> 00:45:30,750
救命啊！

636
00:45:35,521 --> 00:45:37,627
Ellie!
艾莉！

637
00:45:38,047 --> 00:45:40,513
Stay still!
待在那儿，千万别动！

638
00:46:09,848 --> 00:46:12,849
Good thing you're so skinny.
好家伙，我们躲过一劫。

639
00:46:13,574 --> 00:46:16,668
Hey guys, I think it's coming back.

640
00:46:16,703 --> 00:46:20,703
我勒个去，它又回来了

641
00:46:35,032 --> 00:46:36,516
Flairs. They're marking the house.

642
00:46:36,551 --> 00:46:38,000
烟幕弹，他们正在标记这栋房子。

643
00:46:40,890 --> 00:46:44,014
Thanks a lot, Homer.
No one asked your opinion, mate.

644
00:46:44,049 --> 00:46:44,120
非常感谢你，荷马。
没有人在征求你的意见

645
00:46:44,120 --> 00:46:47,244
They know we're here now. -Of course they
know. They saw us through the window.

646
00:46:47,279 --> 00:46:48,877
他们知道我们现在在这里了。
当然他们知道，我打穿了窗户。

647
00:46:48,912 --> 00:46:50,475
But they didn't know we had guns!
但是他们不知道，我们有武器。

648
00:46:53,808 --> 00:46:57,557
Let's get out of here.
C'mon, let's get out of here, now!

649
00:46:57,592 --> 00:46:57,767
我们快离开这里！我们快离开这里！

650
00:46:57,767 --> 00:46:59,850
Go, go, go...
走，走，走

651
00:47:00,892 --> 00:47:03,600
Go, go, move it!

652
00:47:03,635 --> 00:47:04,958
快跑，快跑

653
00:47:05,892 --> 00:47:07,766
Run!

654
00:47:08,392 --> 00:47:10,266
Run!
Flip!

655
00:47:10,372 --> 00:47:12,871
Leave him!
No! 弗林特！

656
00:47:18,833 --> 00:47:19,958
凯文！

657
00:47:21,500 --> 00:47:22,958
来吧！





